description:
In this edition of Beggars Can't Be Cheugers, Jack and Miles discuss the upcoming season of Succession, Mike Lindell's August 13th prediction, a EuroCupdate, NBA news, Nikole Hannah-Jones denying UNC tenure, and Paddington coming back for a third!
